Terrifying dashcam footage has emerged of cars enveloped by a raging wildfire .
At the start visibility for the driver of the car is zero, then intense blue flames emerge through the blanket of smoke and ash .
A jeep with the back of its roof on fire suddenly races past on the right side of the road .
The footage ends with visibility back down to almost nothing .
Wildfires in Siberia have been raging since March 19 .